- Home screen: search bar (by name) + filter chips (status/format) + offline sync indicator
- Ranking: all rows now tappable, navigate to player detail screen
- New player/[id].tsx screen: full stats, match history, head-to-head breakdown
- Profile screen: full match history section (vs, score, competition, V/D badge)
- Competition detail: share button (React Native Share API — text summary)
- Competition detail: admin can rename via long-press on title or ⚙️ menu
- Competition detail: "PRÓXIMO" badge highlights first unplayed match in all view types
- Competition detail: admin "🗑 Apagar placar" button inside ScorerModal (undo score)
- CompetitionsContext: new RENAME action with Firestore sync
- Home: delete confirmation already existed via long-press (unchanged, kept consistent)

